songs.lyrics:
I was messing around in my bedroom
Always this same old boring stuff
So I finally switched on my TV
Hopping to get a tremendous kick
I was certainly dead drunk again
When this foolish movie began
There was a girl looking at me
She took her clothes off and grip my hand
As she said

Kiss me love oh kiss me more
I can't stand to see you crying (x2)

songs.lyrics:
On my way back home after so many times
I wonder how to find my childhood memories
All the fears I had are written on the walls
May the thunder fall burn these ruins down

On my way back home I hear the never ending hum
It brings me back to hell

On my way back home I hear the never ending hum
It brings me back to hell

On my way back home I feel so old
Standing like a stranger staring at the road
Though I know some ways I'm waiting all alone
Now the sun is out I've got to make them pay

On my way back home I hear the never ending hum
It brings me back to hell

On my way back home I hear the never ending hum
It brings me back to hell

album.full_title: 70 Suns in the Sky  by Mary Goes Round

songs.lyrics:
Well it's all right everything's fine
It's nightfall we're having some good time
Far from the land we're walking on the ocean
Where pleasures and drugs will blow our mind aways
We've killed all the dogs so let the silence be
Enjoy the sunset like a new birth
It's a nice trip within your sex
Now I fell in rapture
We shall forget the ugly old man
Dust once he was dust he will be

Hear the sirens song calling calling
We shall follow their sexual attraction
Hear the sirens song calling calling
We shall follow their fatal attraction
Their sexual attraction
Their fatal attraction
Attraction

songs.full_title: The Nile Song by Mary Goes Round
songs.title: The Nile Song

album.full_title: 70 Suns in the Sky  by Mary Goes Round
album.name: 70 Suns in the Sky

annotatable.link_title: The Nile Song by Mary Goes Round
annotatable.title: The Nile Song

songs.lyrics:
I was standing by the Nile
When I saw the lady smile
I would take her out for a while
For a while

Oh, my tears wept like a child
How her golden hair was blowing wild
Then she spread her wings to fly
For to fly

Soaring high above the breezes
Going always where she pleases
She will make it to the islands in the sun

I will follow in her shadow
As I watch her from my window
One day I will catch her eye

She is calling from the deep
Summoning my soul to endless sleep
She is bound to drag me down
Drag me down

songs.title: The Party

annotatable.link_title: The Party by Mary Goes Round
annotatable.title: The Party

songs.lyrics:
Just a party in an empty room
Just a party in an empty room

A light shine in your empty heart
I have to leave you and I don't know why
And I see children playing all around
It just doesn't make any sense

Just a party in an empty room
Just a party in an empty room

I heard a scream in your empty heart
Look at the raven fighting in the fields
The sun is high over your eyes
Just like a glimmer on your silent face
